content.query:
SELECT
    YEAR(lpep_pickup_datetime) AS current_year,
    COUNT(*) AS rides_per_year
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://rayfelipedlgen2account.dfs.core.windows.net/rayfelipedlgen2filesystem/Quickstarts/NYCTripSmall-Feb2022.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) AS [nyc]
GROUP BY YEAR(lpep_pickup_datetime)
ORDER BY 1 ASC
